message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product, which I believe would greatly enhance your experience or needs. Given its high value to me, I understand it might be a bit more than what you're used to paying, but considering its worth, I propose a price of $120. This offer includes not only the product itself but also a limited-time access to exclusive tips and resources that can help you maximize its benefits. I hope you find this proposal appealing. Let me know if you have any questions or need further details.
